data.description: This spacious, energy-efficient home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, 2-car garage and a home office. The community has it all!  This well-maintained home has an open floor plan that connects the kitchen, living room, & dining area which  allows you to keep watch or entertain family and guest while cooking .The primary suite is a haven of tranquility, featuring a more than generous walk-in closet and an ensuite bath. This bath is complete with dual sinks, a relaxing garden tub, and a separate shower for your convenience. This home has luxury vinyl flooring throughout the entire home , yes there is no carpet at all  Relax on the front or rear covered porches ,the choice is yours .  If you’re looking for a master planned community to call home ,the resort-style amenities  such as the fitness center, amazing pools, playgrounds, soccer fields, basketball courts green spaces & on-site schools, and multiple awards make Heartland a must-see option.
